ted from strong earnings, but faced headwinds from sector allocations.</em></p> <p>In November, U.S. equity markets surged to new record highs, marking one of the best monthly performances of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743518-broad-market-gains-shape-moat-strategies-for-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 13:20:00"}, {"id": "4743510", "title": "Chord Energy: Stock Repurchases, Sale Of Assets, Synergies, And Extremely Cheap", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185247646/image_185247646.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Increasing oil prices\" data-id=\"185247646\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"702px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185247646/image_185247646.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185247646/image_185247646.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185247646/image_185247646.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185247646/image_185247646.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185247646/image_185247646.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185247646/image_185247646.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185247646/image_185247646.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185247646/image_185247646.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p cla